item.title: How do i make an ::empty command
item.dc:creator: @Dastan1 Dastan_
item.description:
@Dastan1 wrote:

Add this among your other commands.

[code=cmf]}

	if (command.startsWith("empty")) {
		long now = System.currentTimeMillis();
		if (now - lastAction < 60000) {
			sM("You must wait 60 seconds after an action to ::empty!");
			lastAction = now;
		} else {
			removeAllItems();
		}
	}[/code]
